data.description: THIS COULD BE YOU!!!  Cozy, Quaint, 1 bedroom/ 1 bathroom Condo.  In the heart of DC near Shopping, Metro and Restaurants.  Recently Remodeled, New Flooring, Fresh Paint,  and Bathroom upgrades will make this charming condo a great place to call home!  Off Street Parking in a Secure Parking Lot and Keyed Building Entry will make you feel comfortable along with great neighbors and pleasant grounds.  Washer/ Dryer directly in this unit, make this convenient  city living.  Come take the opportunity to  relax in this cozy condo you can call home..... Or become an investor with a tenant.  Property currently occupied with a tenant.  Tenant is not under a lease but on month-to-month.  New owner selects to re-rent.  Seller Preferred Title:  Worldwide Settlements
